# Accessibility baseline

- Meaningful `alt` on informative images; `alt=""` + `aria-hidden` for decorative-only.
- FAQ / accordions: `aria-expanded`, `aria-controls`, `role="region"` (see `Faq.jsx`).
- Section headings: use `aria-labelledby` when the visible `h2` has an `id`.
- CTA/link text must be descriptive (not “Cliquez ici”).
- Preserve keyboard focus and visible focus styles; do not trap focus in mobile nav.
- External links: `rel="noopener noreferrer"` when `target="_blank"`.

## References

- `src/sections/Faq.jsx`, `src/sections/MetriquesCles.jsx` (heading ids)
- `src/components/Nav.jsx` (mobile menu labels from constants)
